DUNNING PLAYBOOK
Complete guide to recovering failed payments and reducing involuntary churn. 
--- 
WHY DUNNING MATTERS
Failed payments cause 30-50% of all subscription churn Most failed payments are recoverable with the right strategy Subscription businesses lose an estimated $129 billion annually to involuntary churn Effective dunning recovers 50-60% of failed payments 
--- 
