PRE-DUNNING: PREVENT FAILURES BEFORE THEY HAPPEN
CARD EXPIRY MANAGEMENT
Timing Action 30 days before expiry Email: "Your card ending in 4242 expires next month" 15 days before expiry Email: "Update your payment method to avoid interruption" 7 days before expiry Email: "Your card expires in 7 days — update now" 3 days before expiry In-app banner: "Payment method expiring soon" 
