PROVIDER-SPECIFIC SETUP
STRIPE
Enable Smart Retries: 
Dashboard → Settings → Billing → Subscriptions and emails Enable "Smart Retries" under retry rules Set failed payment emails in Dashboard → Settings → Emails 
CODE  144CHARS
Custom retry rules (if not using Smart Retries): 
Webhook events to handle: 
invoice.payment_failed — trigger dunning invoice.paid — cancel dunning, restore access customer.subscription.updated — status changes customer.subscription.deleted — final cancellation 
CHARGEBEE
Built-in dunning: 
Settings → Configure Chargebee → Retry Settings Configure retry attempts and intervals Settings → Configure Chargebee → Email Notifications → Dunning 
Dunning options: 
Automatic retries with configurable schedule Built-in dunning emails (customizable templates) Grace period configuration per plan 
PADDLE
Managed dunning: 
Paddle handles retries and dunning automatically Limited customization (Paddle manages the relationship) Webhook: subscription.payment_failed, subscription.cancelled BF hands-off approach 
RECURLY
Revenue Recovery: 
Configuration → Dunning Management Set retry schedule per plan Configure grace period and final action (pause vs cancel) 
Advanced features: 
Machine-learning retry optimization Per-plan dunning schedules Built-in Account Updater 
