IN-APP DUNNING
Don't rely on email alone. Show payment failures in the app: 
BANNER PATTERN
CODE  228CHARS
Rules: 
Show on every page load during dunning period Allow dismiss (but show again next session) Direct link to payment update (fewest clicks possible) Don't block the product — let them continue using it 
MODAL PATTERN (FOR FINAL WARNING)
CODE  520CHARS
